  [*Il fait beau aujourd'hui, non?*], [The weather is nice today, isn't it?],
  [*Quel temps de chien!*], [What awful weather! (Literally "dog's weather" - a classic Belgian expression)],
  [*Vous avez passé un bon week-end?*], [Did you have a good weekend?],
  [*Quoi de neuf?*], [What's new? (More informal, use with people you know)],
